		<div><h3 class="h1">About ayat</h3><hr></div>
		<div><p>
			Ayat is Afghanistan’s first modest clothing brand providing empowering clothing for work and social. Ayat combines modesty with comfort and style.
			Ayat provides various designs and colors of beautiful clothing for an affordable price for women and girls made by talented Afghan women.
			Now you can be stylish, comfortable and modest at the same time. Ayat was found in 2020 and operates in Kabul, Afghanistan and Bishkek, Kyrgyzstan to provide exceptional modest fashion at an affordable price for the region’s women and girls.
		</p></div>
